   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-a" mid="47" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yeah. (Don't tell her the details.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>You mean you met a man named <FONT color=#a82424>Lapis</FONT> before? And he told you that he's from a land that had been ruined by a Child?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-b" mid="48" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Vernicka will probably know.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Why didn't you tell me earlier? He's bound to have something to do with the Lazuli kingdom! By the way, do you have a way to meet him again?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-b" image="QN_Vernicka.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-c" mid="49" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yeah, I'll go and ask him.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Vernicka</FONT>...? You mean Vernicka, the <FONT color=#a82424>President of Merca City</FONT>?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-2" mid="50" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Phew... she seems a little less agitated now.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Wow I didn't expect you to know him personally. But thank you for taking the initiative to ask him yourself.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-2" image="QN_Vernicka.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Please go and ask <FONT color=#a82424>President Vernicka</FONT> about the man called Lapis.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-a" mid="51" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Ask him if there's a way to meet Lapis.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>What more trouble have you landed yourself upon at a busy time like this?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-b" mid="52" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>I received a report that you met Lapis but it's crazy that you even managed to find out that he's from the Lazuli kingdom.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-c" mid="53" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Anyway, <FONT color=#a82424>April</FONT> wants to know more about the Lazuli kingdom...? The merchant's guild seems to have hushed about it for fear that Lapis's identity might be revealed.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-d" mid="54" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>But I've been keeping an eye on April because she's a smart girl. Maybe this is a chance to reveal a little about the secret networks.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-e" mid="55" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>But please make sure that no other people hears about this. I trust both you and April will not say a word about Lapis to others.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-e" image="QW_107.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3" mid="56" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Go to <FONT color=#a82424>Broken Goldstone Canyon</FONT> where Lapis is residing right now. <BR>You'll be able to find a <FONT color=#a82424>secret calling device</FONT> there.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>After using the <FONT color=#a82424>secret calling device</FONT>, go to the <FONT color=#a82424>deepest end of the mine where the Alicantos are</FONT> and you'll be able to meet Lapis. I'm utterly overburdened with work right now so go now.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-4-a" mid="60" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yeah, I searched everywhere but I couldn't find him.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>What...? You did as I said but Lapis didn't appear?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
